TRANCHE 4 NOW OPEN

Key Investment Features

The Fund is being established to provide a loan secured by a first registered mortgage over a residential development project in Fernvale Queensland comprising 50 land lots that is in the final stages of completion.

The first of three stages has been registered and the first sales have been settled. The loan will be used to refinance existing construction finance, fund the remaining costs to complete and register the last two stages.

The highlights of this project are as follows:

  • Tranche 4 - $5,100,000
  • Total Loan Amount - $5,100,000
  • Fixed Interest - 12% p.a. (Net) paid monthly
  • LVR - varying to a maximum of 60% LVR on balance land unsold
  • 12 months - Principal will begin being repaid from the net proceeds of sales anytime from the first anniversary of the loan. Full repayment of the loan is expected within 24 months.
  • Minimum Investment - $25,000 subject to the Fund Manager’s discretion to reduce this threshold.
  • Security - First registered mortgage

If you would prefer to speak to one of our team members about this offer, please:
Email us at hello@venturecrowd.com.au
Call us at 1300 039 655 NOW!

Investment Structure

You will be investing in a unit trust managed by VentureCrowd Nominees Pty Ltd ACN 166 599 140 in its capacity as trustee for the VentureCrowd Trust No.0501 (Fernvale Developments Pty Ltd) (Trust) as an authorized representative of VentureCrowd Pty Ltd ACN 166 598 849 under Australian Financial Services License No.503381.

Upon making the investment, you will be issued with units in the Trust and you will be able to monitor and manage your investment through your personal dashboard. The Trust is an unregistered unit trust which will lend the proceeds of issue of the units under formal loan documentation to the developer.

Loan repayment will be upon completion of the project and settlement of the sale of the registered land lots.
